modName: Mage Backpack by TumbaJamba for NPCs
summary: Distributes the Mage Backpack by TumbaJamba to the Vigilants of Stendarr or some Winterhold college students, or distributes it to both.
descriptionHtml:
[size=4]Description[/size]
Small add-on which distributes the [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31191/?]Mage Backpack [color=#999999]by TumbaJamba[/color][/url] to the Winterhold College students and the Vigilant of Stendarr. Requires the original mod.
V1.0A Distributes the Mage Backpack to the Vigilants of Stendarr and to some Winterhold College students.
V1.0B Distributes the Mage Backpack to the Vigilants of Stendarr.
V1.0C Distributes the Mage Backpack to the Winterholds College students and former students. Use this version along[size=2][color=#1e84cc] [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/58272/?]Mage Backpack - Retexture[/url][/color][/size][size=2] [/size][color=#999999]by Reptileye[b] [/b][/color]for a more immersive experience.

[size=4]Requirement[/size]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31191/?]Mage Backpack [color=#999999]by TumbaJamba[/color][/url][color=#999999]

[/color]Recommended for version 1.0C[color=#999999]
[/color][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/download/1000127552]Mage Backpack Retexture - MAIN - College of Winterhold flag[/url] [color=#999999]by Reptileye[/color][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/60242/?]
[/url]
[size=4]Compatibility
[/size]This mod is clean and compatible with pretty much everything, you can run [b][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/1840/?]Wrye Bash[/url] [/b]to make it fully compatible with any other mods.

[size=4]Installation
[/size]Simply download with NMM or Mod organizer, or if you prefer you can manually download it.

[size=4]Uninstallation
[/size]Simply use NMM or Mod organizer, or delete MageBackpack_byTumbajambaLeveledList.esp

[size=4]Credits
[/size]All credits go to Bethesda, [size=2]TumbaJamba, DVAted and Reptileye[/size]
